<p>
  You have been invited to collaborate with <%= @message.name %> on a story titled <%= @message.story_title %>.  
  If you would like to accept this invitation, please click here: <%= @message.url %>.
  If you want to decline this invitation, no action is needed on your part.
</p>

<% if @message.message.present? %>
  <p>
    Here is message written to you by <%= @message.name %>:
  </p>

  <%= simple_format @message.message %>
<% end %>

